'''5''' ||[[Pablo Gabriel Garc\u00eda]]\n|-\n|MF ||'''7''' ||[[Gianni Guigou]]\n|-\n|MF ||'''20'''||[[\u00c1lvaro Recoba]]\n|-\n|FW ||'''19'''||[[Javier Chevant\u00f3n]] || ||{{suboff|77}}\n|-\n|FW ||'''11''' ||[[Federico Magallanes]] || ||{{suboff|71}}\n|-\n|colspan=3|'''Substitutions:'''\n|-\n|GK ||'''12'''||[[Gustavo Mun\u00faa]]\n|-\n|DF ||'''14'''||[[Joe Bizera]]\n|-\n|MF ||'''10'''||[[Nicol\u00e1s Olivera]]\n|-\n|MF ||'''16'''||[[Guillermo Giacomazzi]] || ||{{subon|71}}\n|-\n|FW ||'''9''' ||[[Diego Alonso]]\n|-\n|FW ||'''15'''||[[Mario Regueiro]] || ||{{subon|77}}\n|-\n|FW ||'''18'''||[[Richard Morales]]\n|-\n|colspan=3|'''Manager:'''\n|-\n|colspan=\"4\"|[[V\u00edctor P\u00faa]]\n|}\n|}\n{| width=100% style=\"font-size: 90%\"\n| width=50% valign=top|\n'''OFFICIALS'''\n*Assistant referees:\n**[[Marco Ivaldi]] ([[Italian Football Federation|Italy]])\n**[[Aniello Di Mauro]] ([[Italian Football Federation|Italy]])\n*Fourth official: [[Cosimo Bolognino]] ([[Italian Football Federation|Italy]])\n| width=50% valign=top|\n'''MATCH RULES'''\n*90 minutes\n*3 (of 7) [[Substitute (association football)|substitutions]] permitted\n|}\n\n===Second leg===\n{{football box\n| date         = 25 November 2001\n| event        = \n| round        = \n| time         = 16:00 [[UTC\u221203:00|UTC\u22123]]\n| team1        = {{fb-rt|Uruguay}}\n| score        = 3\u20130\n| aet          = \n| report       = [https://www.fifa.com/worldcup/archive/edition=4395/preliminaries/preliminary=8024/matches/match=24860/report.html (Report)]\n| team2        = {{fb|Australia}}\n| goals1       = [[Dar\u00edo Silva|Silva]] {{goal|14}} <br> [[Richard Morales|Morales]] {{goal|70||90}}\n| goals2       = \n| stadium      = [[Estadio Centenario]], [[Montevideo]]\n| attendance   = 62,000\n| referee      = [[Ali Bujsaim]] ([[United Arab Emirates Football Association|UAE]])\n}}\n\n{| width=\"100%\"\n|valign=\"top\" width=\"50%\"|\n{| style=\"font-size: 90%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\"\n|-\n!width=\"25\"